15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 75 O.S. 2021, Section 308.3, as
17 amended by Section 6, Chapter 38, O.S.L. 2023 (75 O.S. Supp. 2024,
18 Section 308.3), is amended to read as follows:
19 Section 308.3. A. The Legislature shall have joint resolutions
20 prepared for consideration each session.
21 B. For the purpose of this section, a proposed permanent rule
22 may be disapproved, in whole or in part, in a joint resolution
23 considered by the Legislature.
